changelog:
## MetaBoost v2.2.0

### New Features
- OpenRouter API integration with multi-provider support (Google Gemini and OpenAI GPT models)
- Added Gemini 3 models support (gemini-3-pro-preview, gemini-3-flash-preview) in Gemini provider
- Added Gemma 3 27B model support in Gemini provider
- Async lazy loading for thumbnail generation

### Improvements
- Improved API key selection with hybrid strategy
- Enhanced rate limiter caching for better performance
- Increased max output tokens for richer metadata

### Bug Fixes
- Fix some bugs
